WEBVTT

00:00.493 --> 00:03.524
I can't believe this
night is finally here.

00:03.534 --> 00:07.309
This is what I've been looking
forward to since I came out.

00:07.319 --> 00:10.220
Good evening, ladies and
gentlemen. I'm Neil Everett..

00:10.230 --> 00:12.623
Welcome to the biggest
night of the year...

00:12.633 --> 00:17.127
All Hallow's Eve, Halloween,
The Gay Super Bowl!

00:17.196 --> 00:20.230
Expectations are high
that this will be...

00:20.299 --> 00:23.167
the biggest and best
Halloween in the history...

00:23.235 --> 00:24.983
of humankind.

00:24.993 --> 00:27.104
This is what it's been all about.

00:27.173 --> 00:30.139
It's a dream come true...
a night where I can totally be me

00:30.208 --> 00:31.208
with no judgment.

